headline: EBay Stock Shows Rising Relative Strength; Rebounding From Dip On Holiday Sales Forecast
summary: Online marketplace eBay saw its stock hit a record high on Aug. 15.  It was within one point of topping it on Oct. 29 when it gave a less than stellar earnings report and fell hard.  EBay stock has rebounded in recent days and may be trying to break that record high again.
